{"tid":1109921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問呢個時期丁可欣嘅支持者係咪都係小學雞？","createTime":"2019-04-16T11:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T11:40:15.000Z","uid":221334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91704865b2a6887797846d15d9a0ffd45bb74732","tid":1109921,"uid":221334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Get0AteTkV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGet0AteTkV4&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c23e49d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Get0AteTkV4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKrLaxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKrLaxb.jpg&h=c2eee350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQ63GDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQ63GDS.jpg&h=fd22a6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33EwQxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33EwQxe.jpg&h=c2c5f1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係youtbe上面見到有人屌火雞姐，結果下面有個叫「獅子座」嘅account不停用小學雞語言屌返佢<br />\n<br />\n我見佢講嘢有錯我咪留言篤爆佢<br />\n<br />\n點知佢就即刻爆氣瘋狂屌返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢對罵之後發覺佢用咗第二個account去幫自己講嘢(行文語氣一模一樣，佢演技真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n再之後仲發覺，佢連火雞姐有道歉影片都唔知， 我真係笑撚咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來唔清楚件事都可以發表意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後碌到去下面，發覺有好多留言都係同呢個小學雞樣講戇鳩嘢<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打如果得閒想要玩鳩佢，歡迎係youtube條片度留言"}]}